MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 212

ESTABLISHING AS PALOMPON WATERSHED FOREST RESERVE A PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITIES OF PALOMPON AND VILLABA, PROVINCE OF LEYTE, PHILIPPINES.

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from entry, sale, disposition or settlement and set aside for watershed and other ecological enhancement purposes, subject to private rights, if there be any, the parcel of land of the public domain located in the Municipalities of Palompon and Villaba, Province of Leyte, Philippines, more particularly described as follows:

